{"tid":514548,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"obama好賤格 連阿伯既感情都呃。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。","createTime":"2017-12-30T16:25:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-31T01:26:57.000Z","uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"525f7c25392d1444072d2b56d170f2871abdb583","tid":514548,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T16:25:00.000Z","msg":"<strong>與相差54歲同性戀人離婚 英退休牧師人財兩空</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/31/002413_25c085d897b583e8fa66d14ef19e9dd9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F31%2F002413_25c085d897b583e8fa66d14ef19e9dd9.jpg&h=47c6a5c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】英國一名79歲牧師退休後與只有25歲的同性戀人結婚，並花掉積蓄於羅馬尼亞為戀人買了大公寓。但兩人結婚半年後就離婚，牧師瞬間失去在羅馬尼亞的房子及自己的積蓄。<br />\n<br />\n退休牧師克萊門茨（Philip Clements）今年4月與同性戀人馬林（Florin Marin）結婚，克萊門茨賣了自己在肯特郡的房子，之後在羅馬尼亞為馬林購買價值近9萬英鎊（約94萬港元）的大公寓。<br />\n<br />\n克萊門茨表示，到羅馬尼亞居住後，由於語言不通，難以交到朋友，感到很寂寞。而馬林就每天都到夜總會消遣，卻不允許克萊門茨跟著去，因馬林指夜總會不適合老人。馬林經常很晚才回家睡覺，有時早上5時就出去，長時間都在外。<br />\n<br />\n兩人經常爭吵，最終於結婚半年後離婚，克萊門茨失去了在羅馬尼亞的房子及自己的積蓄。克萊門茨回到英國後，只能在朋友奶奶丟空的房子中寄居。不過兩人分手後仍保持著聯繫，馬林亦曾飛回英國探望克萊門茨。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%88%87%E7%9B%B8%E5%B7%AE54%E6%AD%B2%E5%90%8C%E6%80%A7%E6%88%80%E4%BA%BA%E9%9B%A2%E5%A9%9A-%E8%8B%B1%E9%80%80%E4%BC%91%E7%89%A7%E5%B8%AB%E4%BA%BA%E8%B2%A1%E5%85%A9%E7%A9%BA-140500716.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E8%2588%2587%25E7%259B%25B8%25E5%25B7%25AE54%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%2590%258C%25E6%2580%25A7%25E6%2588%2580%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%259B%25A2%25E5%25A9%259A-%25E8%258B%25B1%25E9%2580%2580%25E4%25BC%2591%25E7%2589%25A7%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E5%2585%25A9%25E7%25A9%25BA-140500716.html&d=iDzVAHoAp7BrWJAoeKcibdZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=d6dd3b17\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%88%87%E7%9B%B8%E5%B7%AE54%E6%AD%B2%E5%90%8C%E6%80%A7%E6%88%80%E4%BA%BA%E9%9B%A2%E5%A9%9A-%E8%8B%B1%E9%80%80%E4%BC%91%E7%89%A7%E5%B8%AB%E4%BA%BA%E8%B2%A1%E5%85%A9%E7%A9%BA-140500716.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"186dd04a922f0d9df0a47bb4a6d89751d951d2d8","tid":514548,"uid":146924,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T17:45:56.000Z","msg":"好似啲20幾歲大陸雞嫁比阿伯咁<br />\n<br />\n不過呢個係hehe版<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98a4381553a8c0ba73ba6998377e11d9d4628980","tid":514548,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T01:04:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f66f06fe328fd7cc5fd7d0d105c75b30ba84ef0a","tid":514548,"uid":25560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"186dd04a922f0d9df0a47bb4a6d89751d951d2d8","tid":514548,"uid":146924,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T17:45:56.000Z","msg":"好似啲20幾歲大陸雞嫁比阿伯咁<br />\n<br />\n不過呢個係hehe版<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T01:26:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 乜主容許基？"}]}